==2022年總統大選==
小馬可仕於2021年10月5日通過Facebook宣布參選2022年菲律賓總統競選。其妻麗莎在接受媒體採訪時透露，他在觀看電影《[[蟻人_(電影)|蟻人]]》時決定競選總統，<ref name="cnnAntmanPresidentialRun">{{cite news |last1=CNN Philippines Staff |date=2022-03-10 |title=Marcos decides to run for president while watching ‘Ant-Man’, wife reveals |publisher=CNN Philippines |url=https://www.cnnphilippines.com/news/2022/3/10/Bongbong-Marcos-Ant-Man.html |accessdate=2022-05-11 |archive-date=2022-06-08 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20220608080112/https://www.cnnphilippines.com/news/2022/3/10/Bongbong-Marcos-Ant-Man.html }}</ref><ref name="inquirerAntmanPresidentialRun">{{cite news |last1=Mercado |first1=Neil Arwin |date=2022-03-10 |title=Bongbong Marcos was watching ‘Ant Man’ when he decided to run for president, says wife |publisher=Philippine Daily Inquirer |url=https://newsinfo.inquirer.net/1566339/ant-man-inspired-bongbong-marcos-to-run-for-president-says-wife |accessdate=2022-05-11 |archive-date=2022-05-13 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20220513000744/https://newsinfo.inquirer.net/1566339/ant-man-inspired-bongbong-marcos-to-run-for-president-says-wife }}</ref>但小馬可仕表示他並不記得這一刻。<ref>One News PH (March 15, 2022). Did 'Ant-Man' inspire Bongbong Marcos to run for president?. Retrieved April 23, 2022. I'll tell you the truth. I didn't remember that. Because my thoughts were far away. It wasn't just when we were watching in theaters that I was pondering [things].... Actually, when the Boy Abunda interview came out, she mentioned Ant-Man, when we saw each other again, I asked her 'Is that true?'</ref>小馬可仕擔任[[菲律賓聯邦黨|菲律賓聯邦黨]]黨主席，代表該黨參選總統，<ref name="CNN">{{Cite news |last1=Sharma |first1=Akanksha |last2=Westcott |first2=Ben |date=2021-10-06 |title=Ferdinand 'Bongbong' Marcos, son of late dictator, announces Philippines presidential bid |work=CNN |url=https://edition.cnn.com/2021/10/06/asia/philippines-bongbong-marcos-president-bid-intl-hnk/index.html |access-date=2021-10-06 |archive-date=2021-10-06 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20211006055816/https://edition.cnn.com/2021/10/06/asia/philippines-bongbong-marcos-president-bid-intl-hnk/index.html }}</ref>同時也得到其前屬黨[[菲律賓國民黨|菲律賓國民黨]]的支持。<ref>{{Cite news |last=Punzalan |first=Jamaine |date=2021-09-24 |title=Kilusang Bagong Lipunan nominates Bongbong Marcos as 2022 presidential bet |work=ABS-CBN News |url=https://news.abs-cbn.com/news/09/24/21/kbl-nominates-bongbong-marcos-as-2022-presidential-candidate |access-date=2021-10-06 |archive-date=2021-10-06 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20211006155334/https://news.abs-cbn.com/news/09/24/21/kbl-nominates-bongbong-marcos-as-2022-presidential-candidate }}</ref>11月16日，小馬可仕宣布[[杜特蒂|杜特蒂]]總統的女兒為其競選搭檔，也就是[[達沃市|達沃市]]市長[[萨拉·杜特尔特|薩拉·杜特蒂]]。<ref name="INQtandem">{{cite news|last=Mercado|first=Neil Arwin|title=It’s official: Bongbong Marcos, Sara Duterte running in tandem in 2022 elections|url=https://newsinfo.inquirer.net/1515954/breaking-its-official-bongbong-inday-sara-running-as-tandem-for-2022|access-date=2022-04-23|work=Philippine Daily Inquirer|publisher=INQUIRER.net|date=2021-11-16|location=Manila, Philippines|archive-date=2021-11-16|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20211116153120/https://newsinfo.inquirer.net/1515954/breaking-its-official-bongbong-inday-sara-running-as-tandem-for-2022}}</ref>小馬可仕和杜特蒂的配對搭檔命名為“UniTeam”，以標榜“團結”的競選主題<ref name="INQtandem"/>。

在2022年5月大選前，小馬可仕一直在總統調查中保持大幅領先；<ref>{{cite news|last=Baclig|first=Cristina Eloisa|title=The complex role of surveys, public opinion in PH elections|url=https://newsinfo.inquirer.net/1556609/the-complex-role-of-surveys-public-opinion-in-ph-elections|access-date=2022-04-23|work=Philippine Daily Inquirer|publisher=INQUIRER.net|date=2022-02-18|location=Manila, Philippines|archive-date=2022-05-08|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20220508122248/https://newsinfo.inquirer.net/1556609/the-complex-role-of-surveys-public-opinion-in-ph-elections}}</ref><ref>{{cite news|last=Ruiz|first=Ellalyn de Vera|title=Bongbong, Sara still survey frontrunners — Pulse Asia|url=https://mb.com.ph/2022/04/06/bongbong-sara-still-survey-frontrunners-pulse-asia/|access-date=2022-04-23|work=Manila Bulletin|publisher=Manila Bulletin Publishing Corporation|date=2022-04-06|archive-date=2022-06-02|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20220602143730/https://mb.com.ph/2022/04/06/bongbong-sara-still-survey-frontrunners-pulse-asia/}}</ref>是該國1999年民意調查以來，第一位獲得超過 50%民意調查的總統候選人。<ref>{{cite news|last=Ranada|first=Pia|title=Marcos outstrips rivals, Robredo clear second placer in Pulse Asia survey|url=https://www.rappler.com/nation/marcos-outstrips-rivals-robredo-clear-second-placer-pulse-asia-presidential-survey-december-2021/|access-date=2022-04-23|work=Rappler|publisher=Rappler Inc.|date=2021-12-22|location=Manila, Philippines|quote=This is the first time in a Pulse Asia survey that a presidential aspirant got a 'majority vote' equivalent in survey ratings, Pulse Asia executive director Ana Tabunda told Rappler|archive-date=2022-06-02|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20220602040014/https://www.rappler.com/nation/marcos-outstrips-rivals-robredo-clear-second-placer-pulse-asia-presidential-survey-december-2021/}}</ref>但他在總統競選過程中，只曾參加一場[[辯論|辯論]]，受到許多的批評。<ref>{{cite news|last=Mercado|first=Neil Arwin|title=Bongbong Marcos shuns Comelec debates, cites 'preferred mode of communication with people'|url=https://newsinfo.inquirer.net/1568207/bongbong-marcos-shuns-comelec-debates-cites-preferred-mode-of-communication-with-people|access-date=2022-04-23|work=Philippine Daily Inquirer|publisher=INQUIRER.net|date=2022-03-14|location=Manila, Philippines|archive-date=2022-06-02|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20220602045643/https://newsinfo.inquirer.net/1568207/bongbong-marcos-shuns-comelec-debates-cites-preferred-mode-of-communication-with-people}}</ref><ref>{{cite news|last=Galvez|first=Daphne|title=Bello wants Comelec to ‘penalize’ Bongbong Marcos, Sara Duterte for skipping debates|url=https://newsinfo.inquirer.net/1571037/bello-wants-comelec-to-penalize-bongbong-marcos-sara-duterte-for-skipping-debates|access-date=2022-04-23|work=Philippine Daily Inquirer|publisher=INQUIRER.net|date=2022-03-20|location=Manila, Philippines|archive-date=2022-05-11|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20220511052731/https://newsinfo.inquirer.net/1571037/bello-wants-comelec-to-penalize-bongbong-marcos-sara-duterte-for-skipping-debates}}</ref><ref>{{cite news|last1=Carreon|first1=Frencie|last2=Cantal-Albasin|first2=Grace|title=Some Mindanaoans jeer at Marcos for skipping Comelec debate|url=https://www.rappler.com/nation/some-mindanaoans-jeer-marcos-skipping-comelec-debate/|access-date=2022-04-23|work=Rappler|publisher=Rappler Inc.|date=2022-03-20|location=Zamboanga City, Philippines|archive-date=2022-05-12|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20220512052536/https://www.rappler.com/nation/some-mindanaoans-jeer-marcos-skipping-comelec-debate/}}</ref><ref>{{cite news|last=Galvez|first=Daphne|title=Pacquiao keen on attending Comelec debate, if Bongbong Marcos shows up|url=https://newsinfo.inquirer.net/1586655/pacquiao-keen-on-attending-comelec-debate-if-bongbong-marcos-shows-up-too|access-date=2022-04-23|work=Philippine Daily Inquirer|publisher=INQUIRER.net|date=2022-04-22|location=Manila, Philippines|archive-date=2022-06-05|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20220605111558/https://newsinfo.inquirer.net/1586655/pacquiao-keen-on-attending-comelec-debate-if-bongbong-marcos-shows-up-too}}</ref>在5月9日投票截止後的開票過程，小馬可仕取得當選門檻票數，以壓倒性票數領先對手，篤定入主[[馬拉坎南宮|馬拉坎南宮]]，馬可仕家族在歷經36年後重回菲律賓執政，并於同年5月26日獲國會頒發當選證書。<ref>{{cite web |title=菲律賓總統大選 小馬可仕獲壓倒性票數篤定當選總統 |url=https://news.ltn.com.tw/news/world/breakingnews/3921061 |website=自由時報電子報 |accessdate=2022-05-11 |language=zh-TW |date=2022-05-10 |archive-date=2022-05-13 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20220513215430/https://news.ltn.com.tw/news/world/breakingnews/3921061 }}</ref>

